## Quarto

<!-- MSABrowser Demo -->
<section id="MSABrowserDemo"></section>
<!-- end of MSABrowser Demo -->


<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8">
        var viewer;

        $.get("P10636.fa", (fasta) => {

            viewer = new MSABrowser({
                id: "MSABrowserDemo",
                msa: MSAProcessor({
                    fasta: fasta,
                    hasConsensus: true
                }),
                colorSchema: "clustal",
            });

            viewer.export("MSA_export.fasta");

        });
</script>
